quickAddAssets.name: Cesium OSM Buildings
quickAddAssets.description:
A 3D buildings layer derived from OpenStreetMap covering the entire world. It contains over 350 million buildings with per-feature data like name, address, whether a building is commercial or residential, and more.

See the [Cesium OSM Buildings page](https://cesium.com/content/cesium-osm-buildings/) to learn about the available properties and what you can do with this asset.

This tileset is updated monthly. For the latest news, visit our [community forum thread](https://community.cesium.com/t/weve-just-updated-cesium-osm-buildings/10764/last).
